"         wizard\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/burning_hands.md:9
msgid "# Burning Hands _1st-level evocation_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/burning_hands.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action   \n"
"**Range:** Self (15-foot cone)   \n"
"**Components:** V, S   \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/burning_hands.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"As you hold your hands with thumbs touching and fingers spread, a thin sheet "
"of flames shoots forth from your outstretched fingertips. Each creature in a "
"15-foot cone must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d6 fire "
"damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.    \n"
"The fire ignites any flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or "
"carried. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/burning_hands.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above "
"1st.\n"
msgstr ""
